{"tid":1357461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人有種特質，真心問 你地有無？","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:47:23.000Z","uid":153051,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"df46448b738beb92261541feb876a79a33eb183e","tid":1357461,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"香港人有種特質<br />\n 1.平時撘地鐵大家都無友善既感覺<br />\n仲會眼啤啤 啤撚住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.就係發生第一件大件事既時候，<br />\n當再發生另一單大野既同時，<br />\n大家就會集中轉左重心，甚至遺忘左原先既大件事<br />\n<br />\n但重新，我唔係想鬧大家呀，只係我覺得6月開始<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反送中</span></span>呢件事 令大家咁團結<br />\n不論 年紀，身份，地位，職業。<br />\n<br />\n知道呢幾日發生左好多事，<br />\n但點都好<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 我地勿忘初衷 可以嗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n二百萬零一人 上街示威個日，個種感動 <br />\n大家互不相識但樂意去互相幫助，記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n入立法會 示威者點都要帶走義士，大家記得嗎？<br />\n太多感動事，我不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n但我愛香港人！我愛香港！<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講！！！日日唸經咁提醒自己！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求呀！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26406cb2673d948335f82f8f7508a5200899dd67","tid":1357461,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"04a475ae5d3547de2c9b7dfe51c1ceb77fe48ddc","tid":1357461,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"724 地鐵不合作<br />\n<a href=\"htt